(309, '309', 'Electrike', 'Electric', 'https://example.com/images/types/electric.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/bw/electrike.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/audio/cries/electrike.mp3', 'ELECTRIKE stores electricity in its\nlong body hair. This POKéMON stimulates\nits leg muscles with electric charges.These jolts of power give its legs\nexplosive acceleration performance.', 40, 45, 40, 65, 40, 65, 3, 'Electrike, Manectric'),
