(501, '501', 'Oshawott', 'Water', 'https://example.com/images/types/water.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/bw/oshawott.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/audio/cries/oshawott.mp3', 'It fights using the scalchop on its\nstomach. In response to an attack,\nit retaliates immediately by slashing.', 55, 55, 45, 63, 45, 45, 5, 'Oshawott, Dewott, Samurott'),
(502, '502', 'Dewott', 'Water', 'https://example.com/images/types/water.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/bw/dewott.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/audio/cries/dewott.mp3', 'Strict training is how it learns its\nflowing double-scalchop technique.', 75, 75, 60, 83, 60, 60, 5, 'Oshawott, Dewott, Samurott'),
(503, '503', 'Samurott', 'Water', 'https://example.com/images/types/water.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/bw/samurott.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/audio/cries/samurott.mp3', 'One swing of the sword incorporated in\nits armor can fell an opponent. A simple\nglare from one of them quiets everybody.', 95, 100, 85, 108, 70, 70, 5, 'Oshawott, Dewott, Samurott'),
(504, '504', 'Patrat', 'Normal', 'https://example.com/images/types/normal.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/bw/patrat.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/audio/cries/patrat.mp3', 'Using food stored in cheek pouches,\nthey can keep watch for days. They use\ntheir tails to communicate with others.', 45, 55, 39, 35, 39, 42, 5, 'Patrat, Watchog'),
(505, '505', 'Watchog', 'Normal', 'https://example.com/images/types/normal.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/bw/watchog.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/audio/cries/watchog.mp3', 'When they see an enemy, their tails\nstand high, and they spit the seeds of\nberries stored in their cheek pouches.', 60, 85, 69, 60, 69, 77, 5, 'Patrat, Watchog'),
(506, '506', 'Lillipup', 'Normal', 'https://example.com/images/types/normal.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/bw/lillipup.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/audio/cries/lillipup.mp3', 'It faces strong opponents with great\ncourage. But, when at a disadvantage in\na fight, this intelligent Pokémon flees.', 45, 60, 45, 25, 45, 55, 5, 'Lillipup, Herdier, Stoutland'),
(507, '507', 'Herdier', 'Normal', 'https://example.com/images/types/normal.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/bw/herdier.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/audio/cries/herdier.mp3', 'It has black, cape-like fur that is\nvery hard and decreases the amount\nof damage it receives.', 65, 80, 65, 35, 65, 60, 5, 'Lillipup, Herdier, Stoutland'),
(508, '508', 'Stoutland', 'Normal', 'https://example.com/images/types/normal.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/bw/stoutland.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/audio/cries/stoutland.mp3', 'It rescues people stranded by\nblizzards in the mountains. Its\nshaggy fur shields it from the cold.', 85, 110, 90, 45, 90, 80, 5, 'Lillipup, Herdier, Stoutland'),
(509, '509', 'Purrloin', 'Dark', 'https://example.com/images/types/dark.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/bw/purrloin.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/audio/cries/purrloin.mp3', 'They steal from people for fun, but their\nvictims can’t help but forgive them.\nTheir deceptively cute act is perfect.', 41, 50, 37, 50, 37, 66, 5, 'Purrloin, Liepard'),
(510, '510', 'Liepard', 'Dark', 'https://example.com/images/types/dark.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/bw/liepard.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/audio/cries/liepard.mp3', 'These Pokémon vanish and appear\nunexpectedly. Many Trainers are drawn\nto their beautiful form and fur.', 64, 88, 50, 88, 50, 106, 5, 'Purrloin, Liepard'),
(511, '511', 'Pansage', 'Grass', 'https://example.com/images/types/grass.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/bw/pansage.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/audio/cries/pansage.mp3', 'This Pokémon dwells deep in the forest.\nEating a leaf from its head whisks\nweariness away as if by magic.', 50, 53, 48, 53, 48, 64, 5, 'Pansage, Simisage'),
(512, '512', 'Simisage', 'Grass', 'https://example.com/images/types/grass.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/bw/simisage.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/audio/cries/simisage.mp3', 'Ill tempered, it fights by swinging its\nbarbed tail around wildly. The leaf\ngrowing on its head is very bitter.', 75, 98, 63, 98, 63, 101, 5, 'Pansage, Simisage'),
(513, '513', 'Pansear', 'Fire', 'https://example.com/images/types/fire.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/bw/pansear.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/audio/cries/pansear.mp3', 'When it is angered, the temperature\nof its head tuft reaches 600° F.\nIt uses its tuft to roast berries.', 50, 53, 48, 53, 48, 64, 5, 'Pansear, Simisear'),
(514, '514', 'Simisear', 'Fire', 'https://example.com/images/types/fire.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/bw/simisear.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/audio/cries/simisear.mp3', 'It loves sweets because they become\nenergy for the fire burning inside\nits body.', 75, 98, 63, 98, 63, 101, 5, 'Pansear, Simisear'),
