(993, '993', 'Ironjugulis', 'Dark, Flying', 'https://example.com/images/types/dark.png, https://example.com/images/types/flying.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/sprites/bw/ironjugulis.png', 'https://play.pokemonshowdown.com/audio/cries/ironjugulis.mp3', 'It resembles a certain Pokémon introduced in a paranormal magazine, described as the offspring of a Hydreigon that fell in love with a robot.', 94, 80, 86, 122, 80, 108, 9, 'Iron-jugulis');
